    <bioghist encodinganalog="MARC 545"> 
      <head altrender="organization" id="a2">ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY </head> 
      <p>Gavras was one of the four original Finger Lakes Runners Club members
        listed on the club charter. He was a competitive masters runner who competed
        on a Finger Lakes Runners Club masters team all over the United States and in
        Europe and continued to run into his 80's.</p> 
    </bioghist> 
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520"> 
      <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head> 
      <p>Includes newspaper articles and magazines concerning running; meet
        results and awards.</p> 
    </scopecontent> 
